{"tid":1759670,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"咦？區議會大勝，是咪我地已經可以成立獨立調查委員會？","createTime":"2019-11-27T20:05:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-27T20:22:16.000Z","uid":280192,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ddd710fbdd548018820ecf50958ae576b824d23f","tid":1759670,"uid":280192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-27T20:05:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8B%95%E8%AD%B0%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-721%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E5%90%A6%E6%B1%BA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-721%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%25B1%25BA%2F&d=iBLSwy1tqwhlDNpwtuM9DapJ2kzo9njAZIZZFH2Kh%2FI%3D&h=6471c937\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E7%258D%25A8%25E7%25AB%258B%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-721%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E8%25A5%25B2%25E6%2593%258A-%25E5%2585%2583%25E6%259C%2597%25E5%258D%2580%25E8%25AD%25B0%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2590%25A6%25E6%25B1%25BA%2F&h=71a43a7b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E5%8B%95%E8%AD%B0%E7%8D%A8%E7%AB%8B%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-721%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E8%A5%B2%E6%93%8A-%E5%85%83%E6%9C%97%E5%8D%80%E8%AD%B0%E6%9C%83%E5%90%A6%E6%B1%BA/</a><br />\n<br />\n好記得上面單新聞，之前元朗區議會被pk親中少數派議員把持，否決左調查7.21。<br />\n咁是咪代表，宜家各區議會可以正式動用各方面人力物力資源，調查各區警察濫權問題？當警察不斷亂入屋村亂打人亂放催淚彈，係直接影響各區居民安全和營商環境。<br />\n<br />\n就算我地無權傳召證人或定罪，區議會起碼可以請資深法官，搞一份有公信力嘅報告，將事件先在民間和法律界定性，然後向全世界公告，咁應該做得到架播。<br />\n<br />\n只要我地先做一個有規模嘅獨立調查，情況就好似開民間記者會咁，政府如果唔想被搶走話語權，就要官方都搞返一個獨立調查抗衡。<br />\n<br />\n咁獨立調查呢個訴求，就可以前進一大步。"},{"pid":"863adc35682611fea9dc7b6573905e6f9d409554","tid"